headline: Is Sempra (SRE) Attractive After Strong 1-Year Rally And Capital Project Focus?
summary: If you are wondering whether Sempra’s current share price lines up with its underlying value, you are not alone. This article is built to help you weigh what you are paying against what you are getting. Sempra’s stock last closed at US$95.20, with returns of 2.4% over the past week, 9.3% over the past month, 6.1% year to date and 36.7% over the past year, alongside 3 year and 5 year returns of 41.0% and 90.9% respectively.
